---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import LandingPageLayout from "src/layouts/LandingPageLayout.astro";
import CallToAction from "src/components/CallToAction.astro";
---

<LandingPageLayout
  title="A Storyblok developer backed by Storyblok themselves"
  metaTitle="Storyblok developer | Storyblok consultant Yorkshire | Rob Kendal, Storyblok partner"
  description="As a Storyblok developer based in Wakefield and Leeds, West Yorkshire. I build Storyblok websites and help with Storyblok consultancy projects."
  brands={{
    title: 'Great brands; amazing teams!',
    intro:
      "As an experienced Storyblok developer, I've worked with some amazing Yorkshire companies and some big national brands",
  }}
  testimonials={{
    title: 'Winning projects means happy users',
    intro:
      "From Storyblok website development and Storyblok content platform design, here's what some of the teams I've worked with have to say.",
  }}
>
  <Fragment slot="intro">
    If you've been on the hunt for a trusted, reliable <strong>Storyblok developer</strong> 
    based in Wakefield and Leeds, to help with website and web app development
    powered by Storyblok, content platform design, and Storyblok migrations,
    then read on.
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="intro-content">
    <div class="rounded-sm bg-blue-50 p-4 mt-10 mb-28">
      <div class="flex">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <svg
            class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400"
            viewBox="0 0 20 20"
            fill="currentColor"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a.75.75 0 000 1.5h.253a.25.25 0 01.244.304l-.459 2.066A1.75 1.75 0 0010.747 15H11a.75.75 0 000-1.5h-.253a.25.25 0 01-.244-.304l.459-2.066A1.75 1.75 0 009.253 9H9z"
              clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="ml-3 text-xl text-blue-700 space-y-3">
          <p>
            <strong class="text-blue-700">
              I'm no longer taking on new freelance projects
            </strong>. 
          </p>
          <p>
            I'm looking to move away from freelance work to focus on building 
            software products as part of a larger team. If you're looking for an
            experienced software developer to join your team, please do reach out
            and we can see if there's a fit!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="hireme">
    Tell me about your Storyblok project and see if I could be a great addition to your team.
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="cta">
    <CallToAction
      type="global"
      title="Hire a Storyblok developer with a track record of success"
      buttons={[
        {
          href: '/contact',
          text: 'discuss your project',
        },
      ]}
    >
      If you're in need of a senior Storyblok developer for your project or digital product
      then let's see how I could join your team and make that happen.
    </CallToAction>
  </Fragment>
</LandingPageLayout>
